ibution in the cities of Bhiwandi, Agra, and Shil-Mumbra-Kalwa covering an area of approximately 1,007 square kilometers. In addition, the company is involved in the manufacture and supply of power cables and ancillary services. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Ahmedabad, India. Torrent Power Limited is a subsidiary of Torrent Investments Limited."}}